  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Ulcus cruris venosoum

          -  AAI &gt; 0.9

          -  age 18-80

          -  adress Oslo area

          -  wound size 2.5-100 cm2

          -  wound duration &gt; 6 weeks.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Diabetes mellitus

          -  Immunosuppresion

          -  antibiotics &lt; 14 days

          -  local antiseptic treatment &lt; 1 week

          -  clinical infection.
